reason for clozapines high cost is the need for patients to 
undergo weekly blood tests to check for a potentially deadly side 
effect a reduction in white blood cell count 
the company estimates 5000 patients in public and private 
hospitals in the united states take clozapine sandoz 
pharmaceuticals estimated up to 2 percent of patients taking the 
drug could develop the side effect 
the price of the drug should drop when more psychiatrists 
prescribe it said dr gilbert honigfeld a sandoz spokesman 
