miner vladimir bludov stood up nine minutes into the congress and 
called for the party leadership to resign and on day 10 when 
boris yeltsin strode into the palace of congresses and stunned a 
hushed crowd by saying he was quitting the party the speech drew 
derisive whistles and shouts of shame 
